title: Lakers Tonight with Jason Timpf - What to make of LeBron's historic night and more Russ rumors
itunes:title: Lakers Tonight with Jason Timpf - What to make of LeBron's historic night and more Russ rumors
description:
Jason gives his take on LeBron's 56-point performance, the reported rift among the Lakers about sending Russ to the bench, why the Warriors are struggling so much and what the key difference is between Luka and Harden.
